trans-unit.source: Provides an interface that can look up information about the types used in the current Web Forms project.
trans-unit.target: 提供可以查閱目前 Web Form 專案所使用之類型資訊的介面。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager> interface is obsolete.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager> 介面已經過時。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager> class for equivalent designer functionality.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager>對等的設計工具功能的類別。

trans-unit.source: A Web Forms document designer must implement this interface.
trans-unit.target: Web Form 文件設計工具必須實作這個介面。

trans-unit.source: Implementing this interface enables a designer to manage references and provide information related to Web Forms controls within the project.
trans-unit.target: 實作這個介面可讓設計工具來管理的參考，並提供在專案中的 Web Form 控制項的相關資訊。

trans-unit.source: The tag prefix for the type.
trans-unit.target: 型別的標記前置詞。

trans-unit.source: The name of the type.
trans-unit.target: 型別的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the specified object.
trans-unit.target: 取得指定物件的型別。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the object, if it could be resolved.
trans-unit.target: 物件的 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> (當可以解析它時)。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager.GetObjectType%2A> method is obsolete.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager.GetObjectType%2A>方法已過時。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager.GetType%2A> method on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager> class for equivalent designer functionality.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager.GetType%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager>對等的設計工具功能的類別。

trans-unit.source: Gets the register directives for the current project.
trans-unit.target: 取得目前專案的登錄指示詞。

trans-unit.source: The register directives for the current project.
trans-unit.target: 目前專案的登錄指示詞。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager.GetRegisterDirectives%2A> method is obsolete.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager.GetRegisterDirectives%2A>方法已過時。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager.GetRegisterDirectives%2A> method on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager> class for equivalent designer functionality.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager.GetRegisterDirectives%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager>對等的設計工具功能的類別。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object.
trans-unit.target: 物件的類型。

trans-unit.source: Gets the tag prefix for the specified type of object.
trans-unit.target: 取得指定物件型別的標記前置詞。

trans-unit.source: The tag prefix for the specified object type, if it could be located.
trans-unit.target: 指定物件型別的標記前置詞 (如存在時)。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager.GetTagPrefix%2A> method is obsolete.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IWebFormReferenceManager.GetTagPrefix%2A>方法已過時。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager.GetTagPrefix%2A> method on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager> class for equivalent designer functionality.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager.GetTagPrefix%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsReferenceManager>對等的設計工具功能的類別。
